Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.45,0:02:06.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She denied our help.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.72,0:02:08.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.56,0:02:12.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You just said you're headed home\Nbecause you finished the job!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.53,0:02:14.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's what\Nwe were planning to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.20,0:02:17.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But we passed a fire\Nengine on the way back
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.40,0:02:20.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We got concerned\Nand headed back to the residence...
