Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.17,0:08:35.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's melted from the heat of the fire but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.81,0:08:37.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe somebody was\Nmounted on this horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.11,0:08:40.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The military commander\Nthat was riding the Red Rabbit Horse was,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.98,0:08:41.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,who was he...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.12,0:08:45.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,K.Kanu!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.95,0:08:46.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh, Kanu?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.42,0:08:47.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh. Kanu?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.55,0:08:48.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's really suspicious after all,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.02,0:08:51.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,that timid man with\Nthe round rim glasses!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.16,0:08:54.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kanu is the god of prosperity in business!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.10,0:08:57.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The key holder box\Nthat the man tried to give away is
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.03,0:09:00.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,just the right size for this too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.17,0:09:02.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no doubt about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.70,0:09:05.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The guy thatrwas riding\Nthe Red Rabbit Horse was...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.91,0:09:07.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We don't have time to waste!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.58,0:09:11.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's call all the antique\Nshops in the vicinity of Haidocho!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.05,0:09:13.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'd better hurry or he'll get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.35,0:09:20.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I hope:-that the man\Nyou guys say you saw isn't him...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.69,0:09:24.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh no! It's already past 23:00!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.99,0:09:28.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're all supposed to go to\NTropical Land tomorrow and yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.21,0:09:30.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe they aren't\Nplanning to come home?
