Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.97,0:11:51.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, no not really
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.41,0:11:56.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't get so angry. Ran,\Nwe can't go home for a while longer
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.41,0:11:57.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dang ou.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.68,0:12:00.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh yes, you were pretty knowledgeable\Nabout the story Sangokushi, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.68,0:12:01.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y.Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.25,0:12:04.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The military commander\Nwho was mounted on the
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.85,0:12:06.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Red Rabbit Horse\Nwas called "Ryofu right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.85,0:12:09.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,'Right! But. later the horse\Nwas given to "Soso
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.86,0:12:12.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and in the end. it went to\NKanu', who was the last to own it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.43,0:12:13.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you sure about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.53,0:12:16.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, because the key\Nholder I was iven of Kanu
