Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.34,0:12:29.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm asking you what's the address?\NWhat chome is it on?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.04,0:12:31.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,F.Fifth chome...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.28,0:12:34.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,O. Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.25,0:12:36.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's Pops doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.65,0:12:40.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure. but he said for us to not\Ngo outside and stay in the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.16,0:12:47.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh great. I've been hearing strange\Nnoises from the front door
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.44,0:12:58.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?! Genda lives in Rizencho?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.77,0:13:01.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?! Genda lives in Rizencho?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.61,0:13:04.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, what about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.53,0:13:07.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When Ryoko's husband came b\Nack home at about 7:20 pm.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.75,0:13:11.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We saw Mr. Genda near\Nthe house in Haidocho
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.99,0:13:13.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The bus that Ran rode is\Nprobably the one that
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.99,0:13:18.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,goes from Haidocho via Beikacho\Nand then to Rizencho
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.06,0:13:22.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Although it's true that\NMr. Genda intended to go home once,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.33,0:13:25.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,for one reason or another,\Nhe returned to that house!
