Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.77,0:13:29.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rizencho is the place where\Nthe first fire occurred, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.74,0:13:33.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, the house that\Nburned was right near his...
