Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.04,0:13:37.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,as well as a good customer\Nof his shop...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.05,0:13:41.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which means that the real\Nreason he set fire to the house
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.25,0:13:42.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,was to hide the fact that the\Nitem that he sold was fake,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.15,0:13:46.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and before anyone found out,\Nhe burned the house down
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.42,0:13:47.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.12,0:13:49.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, I don't understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.96,0:13:53.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you detain him at the station\Nbeing as suspicious as he was?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.93,0:13:58.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess the intuition of a\Npolice detective within me
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.07,0:14:00.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,has gotten rusty...
