Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.52,0:14:20.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Heijr.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.45,0:14:21.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.96,0:14:25.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After the phone call just a\Nwhile ago. that man came here,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.66,0:14:28.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and asked to have the key holder\Nthat he gave us in the bus back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.63,0:14:30.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We asked him why and he said...
