Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.99,0:15:00.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll take the suspect over to the Beika\NPolice Department for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.66,0:15:01.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y. Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.90,0:15:10.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Judging from the looks of it, it\Nseems he'll spit it out right away
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.64,0:15:14.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey. Hattori. doesn't this resemble
