Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.88,0:15:21.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The renown Detective Poalo series.\NA masterpiece of all masterpieces!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.62,0:15:25.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's just like The ABC Murders!"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.10,0:15:28.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The killer kills people who have the\Nsame initials as the name of the
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.89,0:15:31.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,place and kills them off\None by one in order of ABC
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.78,0:15:36.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then an ABC time schedule is\Nplaced near the corpse to
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.06,0:15:38.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,make it look as if it were\Nthe doings of a serial killer
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.45,0:15:45.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And finally he kills the\Nactual target "C" that he is after.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.37,0:15:48.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He hides the orderliness of a\Nplanned murder under the guise
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.63,0:15:52.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,of a disorderly random murder.\NIt sure is similar!
