Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.09,0:16:10.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems that we'd\Nbetter look into this a little deeper
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.93,0:16:15.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'd better check out the sites of the fire\Nof 4-chome that smells of tricks involved
