Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.49,0:16:35.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know if it's topical or\Npickles, but this case(is sure
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.76,0:16:38.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,going to put us in a\Npickle if we don't solve it fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.73,0:16:43.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Case, but the arsonist was arrested\NIast night{ wasn't he
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.26,0:16:46.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah! The man with the round rimmed
