Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.39,0:17:08.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And. Keiko Gondo is a fortuneteller!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.79,0:17:12.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All three of them seem to be able\Nto manipulate the hearts of people,
