Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.61,0:17:31.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's kind of eerie.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.18,0:17:34.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really, I can't understand the\Nfeeling of somebody who
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.01,0:17:35.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,wants toicome to a scary place like this
