Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.93,0:17:53.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And. Did Genda confess?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.37,0:17:56.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His answer is an unchanging,\NI don't know."
