Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.41,0:18:03.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,According to him, he says\Nthere's another him within himself
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.54,0:18:07.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and that guy may be\Ngoing around setting fire.
