Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.25,0:18:16.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so he'sgbeen seeing a\Ndoctor for treatment
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.69,0:18:18.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A.And don't tell me his doctor is...
