Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.30,0:18:30.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, he looked really surprised at hearing\Nthat Genda was the arsonist
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.94,0:18:34.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, the man\Ncalled Soga also looked surprised
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.08,0:18:38.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Soga and Genda used to see each\Nother a lot at the antique marketplace
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.35,0:18:41.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And Sega seems to be the one who
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.05,0:18:42.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,recommended Genda to\Ngo to Morozumi's hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.15,0:18:45.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Misao Soga is an odd character who\Nquit the medical university part
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.52,0:18:48.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,way and got absorbed in Eeng Shun
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.56,0:18:51.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The reason why Genda was in that area that\Nday was because Soga had told him that
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.79,0:18:58.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,if he goes 10 the houses; there, the direction\Nis good.so he might-find some luck...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.27,0:19:03.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, just as Hieji had said,\Nhe had some connection with Mr. Genda!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.90,0:19:06.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which means that Genda may\Nhave some connection
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.31,0:19:09.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,with the fortune éller KeikoGondo too...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.68,0:19:12.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No. I haven't gone that far yet. but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.51,0:19:14.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,that lady smells fishy...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.11,0:19:19.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When Ryoko was found, I saw her\Ngripping this small cushion really hard .
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.95,0:19:23.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I had them all come this morning\Nto headquarters and asked them
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.42,0:19:26.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,if this looked familiar to them,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.13,0:19:31.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but only that woman Gondo turned pale\Nand left in the wink of an eye...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.90,0:19:34.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that a dying messagej?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.54,0:19:36.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why did you let her go?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.74,0:19:38.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The arsonist had already confessed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.41,0:19:42.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And that lady already had an alibi\NSO we couldn't detain her...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.18,0:19:47.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, that's only if the time of\Nthe arson is correct as you both insist.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.61,0:19:49.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, would you like\Nto confirm for yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.52,0:19:52.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The one who testified is\Nthe boy next door...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.26,0:19:57.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really. it's really true!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.52,0:19:58.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I saw it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.23,0:20:01.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When the opening song\Nof Kamen Yaiba started
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.70,0:20:05.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I saw a large shadow of a horse\Non the curtain of the living room!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.87,0:20:07.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is it true ma'am?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.63,0:20:08.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.60,0:20:13.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,because I entered the living room at 7:30\Nind turned on the lights right away...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.67,0:20:15.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so I'm not sure if there was\Na shadow there or not...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.34,0:20:16.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.18,0:20:19.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Will you show us that room?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.68,0:20:22.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's this room. eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.72,0:20:26.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If so.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.19,0:20:29.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The shadow of the horse was\Nprojected on this curtain...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.73,0:20:34.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,True...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.80,0:20:35.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,True...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.26,0:20:38.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, why was your:ison watching\NTV in a dark:room 7 .
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.27,0:20:42.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems all the kids in\Nthis neighborhood do so now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.44,0:20:45.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's like watching a movie and really cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.21,0:20:49.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But sonny... make sure you turn on\Nthe'lights whenfyou watch TV. okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.61,0:20:51.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, our eyes will go\Nbad really quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.01,0:20:53.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just like him?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.78,0:21:01.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe the shadow of the horse\Nwas already projected before 7:30...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.29,0:21:07.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The shadow that is createdyby flames\Nget light and dark and sways a lot too. so
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.29,0:21:10.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,you can't tell if it's a horse or not at times.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.36,0:21:12.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.87,0:21:16.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because I was watching\Nbaseball all the while
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.10,0:21:18.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,until the clock on top of the TV\Nstruck the time for Kamen Yaiba but...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.14,0:21:22.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It got really bright outside\Nthe window and I saw the shadow.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.74,0:21:25.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was time for the Kamen Yaiba song.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.01,0:21:28.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,'Hen were you watching the baseball\Ngame with the room dark too?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.78,0:21:33.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But; if it's dark you can't see\Nthe time of the clock. right...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.39,0:21:37.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I could see it because\Nit was dimly light outside the window...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.13,0:21:42.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Besides. the shadow of\Nthe horse wasn't swaying.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.13,0:21:47.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Heiji!?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.40,0:21:48.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.17,0:21:50.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look really closely for it Hattori!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.94,0:21:52.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sure it's somewhere!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.71,0:21:53.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.59,0:21:56.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The evidence that will prove our\Ndeduction, is here some place for sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.18,0:21:58.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.31,0:22:00.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's an incandescent electric light bulb!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.28,0:22:02.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've found one here too!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.22,0:22:06.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here and there in.burnt places,\Nthere are burnt remains of tissue paper...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.72,0:22:08.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which means that...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.32,0:22:10.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, if this trick is used,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.99,0:22:13.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,you don't have to be here\Nto set fire to the place!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.46,0:22:19.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All we need to find out now is\Nhow the culprit manipulated Mr Genda...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.60,0:22:21.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've got to find proof of that...
